casebody.data:
Tuesday, September 27, 1994

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

93-545. Columbia Gas of Ohio, Inc. v. Limbach.

Board of Tax Appeals, No. 90-M-537. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Board of Tax Appeals. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application be, and the same is hereby, granted.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
